  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_03.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shaman causes a creature within 30 feet to become slightly magnetic until the end of the shaman’s next turn. Whenever the creature is attacked with a melee or ranged weapon constructed primarily of metal, it takes a –2 penalty to AC.</p>\n<p>At 8th and 16th levels, the penalty increases by –2 and the duration extends by 1 round.</p>\n<p>Once affected, the creature cannot be the target of this hex again for 24 hours.</p>"
